      <title>据称法国农业信贷银行将主导对法国兴业银行旗下汉萨银行的竞购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/credit-agricole-said-to-lead-bidding-for-socgen-s-hanseatic-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 正在就收购法国兴业银行 (Societe Generale SA) 旗下德国消费金融业务汉萨银行 (Hanseatic Bank) 进行深入谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/credit-agricole-said-to-lead-bidding-for-socgen-s-hanseatic-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 16:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陷入困境的交易商寻求恢复正常，ADM 任命 3M 首席财务官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/adm-hires-3m-cfo-patolawala-as-crop-trader-seeks-return-to-normal-after-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿彻丹尼尔斯米德兰公司 (Archer-Daniels-Midland Co.) 正努力摆脱会计丑闻，已聘请了 3M 公司的一名高管来监督其财务状况并帮助恢复其在股东心目中的信誉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/adm-hires-3m-cfo-patolawala-as-crop-trader-seeks-return-to-normal-after-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 15:24:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco 警告信贷市场回报未能弥补风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/pimco-warns-credit-market-returns-fail-to-compensate-for-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司称，由于更多的资本追逐太少的机会抑制了回报，投资者在信贷市场借贷风险所获得的补偿不足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/pimco-warns-credit-market-returns-fail-to-compensate-for-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
